snippet.textDisplay: How are they laughing about it being Kim and Kendall’s fight. Kim did the same thing that made Kendall upset to Kourtney. Except in a manner that was worse. Kim repeatedly kept referencing and trying to make it obvious that Kourtney was lazy. If it would make Kendall upset and want to get into it with Kim, why are they ‘surprised’ that it made Kourtney upset. Especially when it’s a jab she has to constantly endure from Kim... It’s unfortunate that they are allowing themselves to misunderstand her like this. Even if she’s angry all the time, remember, the people who seem least lovable tend to be the ones that need love the most. She’s probably going through something and instead of being there for her, they’re ostracising her and putting her down. They are forgetting to be her sisters... Their priorities seem to be misaligned and it’s just poor.
